	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">CodeDebt</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent">
		<h3 id="siteSub">From SPA Wiki</h3>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="index.php?title=CodeDebt#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="index.php?title=CodeDebt#searchInput">search</a></div>
		<!-- start content -->
<p>Thanks to all (35!) of you who turned up in a small room to participate in this session (<a href="http://www.spaconference.org/spa2008/sessions/session165.html" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.spaconference.org/spa2008/sessions/session165.html</a>)! There are a couple of photos at the end (see more at <a href="http://www.flickr.com/groups/spa2008photos/" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.flickr.com/groups/spa2008photos/</a>) to remind you that the best parties happen in the smallest kitchens...
</p><p><i>Peter &amp; David</i>
</p>
<hr />
